<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 各位考生和家长们： &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本科和专科志愿填报即将开始啦！在认真研读《河南省2025年招生之友》后，我们为大家梳理了我校在报刊的页码数，方便大家查看。</strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751270602213.png" alt="1751270602213.png" data-href="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751270602213.png" style=""> </p><p style="text-align: center;"> &nbsp; </p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(225, 60, 57);"><strong> </strong></span><span style="color: rgb(225, 60, 57); font-size: 19px;"><strong>本科</strong></span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><strong> &nbsp;历史类 437页 </strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751270626208.jpg" alt="1751270626208.jpg" data-href="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751270626208.jpg" style="width: 716.00px;height: 1005.04px;"> <strong> &nbsp; </strong> &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(225, 60, 57); font-size: 19px;"><strong> 本科</strong></span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><strong> 物理类 第581页</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751271298034.jpg" alt="1751271298034.jpg" data-href="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751271298034.jpg" style="width: 736.00px;height: 1038.57px;"><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; </p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong> &nbsp;</strong> &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(225, 60, 57); font-size: 19px;"><strong>专科</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(225, 60, 57); font-size: 19px;"> </span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><strong>历史类 &nbsp;第617-618页 </strong></span><strong> </strong> &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center;"> &nbsp; <img src="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751270693129.jpg" alt="1751270693129.jpg" data-href="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751270693129.jpg" style="width: 693.00px;height: 972.69px;"> <strong> &nbsp;</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(225, 60, 57); font-size: 19px;"><strong>专科</strong></span><span style="font-size: 19px;"> &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><strong> 物理类 &nbsp;第739页 </strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><img src="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751270721095.jpg" alt="1751270721095.jpg" data-href="https://zhaosheng.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1751270721095.jpg" style="width: 691.00px;height: 974.99px;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </p><p style="text-align: center;"> &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"> </span><span style="color: rgb(225, 60, 57); font-size: 16px;"> </span><span style="color: rgb(225, 60, 57); font-size: 19px;">【高考填报倒计时】河南普通批次志愿填报即将开启！6月30日8:00-7月3日18:00（本科批次）；7月5日8:00-7月7日18:00（专科批次），家长考生速填！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"> &nbsp;江西软件职业技术大学招生办 &nbsp;编 辑 | 胡龙欣 审编 &nbsp;| 薛利锋 终审 &nbsp;| 沈万红</p>